tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
context: Full Mouth Rehabilitation,RCT - Root Canal Treatment,Cosmetic/ Aesthetic Dentistry,Zirconia Crowns,Smile Design,
review:
I had been to quite a few dentists over the past decade.
And good amount of dentistry has been done in my mouth.
But I was never satisfied with the end result and the bits and pieces dentistry didn't help either.

Someone referred me to Dr. Manish and in the first visit itself, he saw the whole picture and explained the situation to me. It was very impressive and made a lot of sense.
A month later, after some old dental work replacement and some new, I have a brand new smile and I love it.
best part about the whole treatment was that he knew the end in mind before starting the treatment and he even gave me a test/trial run.

Absolutely meticulous and neat, the treatment was painless and planned to perfection.
Dr. Manish and his team made me feel comfortable throughout the treatment and his clinic is extremely hi tech with modern equipment and  machines, all under one roof. 

Highly highly recommend.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
context: RCT - Root Canal Treatment,Ceramic Crowns and Bridges Fixing,Tooth Coloured Fillings,Smile Design,
review:
I visited Dr. Manish as a friend of mine referred me to him.
I was pleasantly surprised in the first visit itself. 
The vibes in the clinic are so good and he instantly made me feel comfortable and assured me that my pain and other issues will be taken care of.
After check up and x ray, he explained the problem and the solutions available and most importantly answered all my questions patiently which is so rare. The subsequent appointments and the whole treatment went perfectly as planned - painless and smooth.

I am extremely satisfied and very happy with the experience.
Another point to note is that his clinic is equipped with every machine you can think of...... high end chair, full mouth x ray machine, lasers and the latest digital scanner.

Highly recommended.
